// rosetta · circuits.full.symbols.dl — legible twin (token STRINGS) of the n-gram cover; inherits the certificate.
// NOTE: this model also carries STRUCTURAL circuits (induction, once_appearing, succession) — computations over token identity/
// order/ordinal, not token lookups, so they are not representable as symbol facts; see circuits.full.dl.

.decl tok(inst:number, pos:number, sym:symbol)
.input tok
.decl mp(inst:number, m:number)
mp(I,M) :- tok(I,_,_), M = max P : { tok(I,P,_) }.
